TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed HttpRequestHeader extends System.Enum

Docs.summary: The HTTP headers that may be specified in a client request.

remarks.format: ## Remarks The appropriate contents of various headers are described in detail in the HTTP/1.1 specification, available at [rfc2616](http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616.html).
